Above and below the waterfall.
cc: @matt_swack

As if you can meditate here.😍😍
So calming 😍🤩
I wish we could smell the air of this scenery 🤩 such a beautiful and clean video

Nature shows us
1st half of our life: Noise 
2nd half of our life: Calmness
So whimsical, magical and beautiful. I adore nature 💚💙
People: oh so beautiful nature is so calming Meanwhile the cgi artist who made this clip 🗿🗿🗿
